items.title: Imran Khan and wife given further jail terms after state gift fraud case
items.description: Pakistan's former PM, who is already serving time in prison, plans to challenge the verdict.

items.title: Watch: Images, cassettes and high-profile figures from Epstein files

items.title: US carries out 'massive' strike against IS in Syria
items.description: The US says it struck dozens of targets across Syria in response to last week's deadly Islamic State attack on US forces there.

items.title: Australian state plans to ban intifada chants after Bondi shooting

items.title: 'Very cool': The 70s Afro-rock genre enjoying a surprising rebirth
items.description: In 1970s Zambia, Zamrock led a musical revolution. It's now back, with some big names among its proponents.
